Some children speak at night
I do not mean those who wake up and tell us something that happened the day before, but the children who talk during sleep.
When it happens to you for the first time, at best you will be terrified, but in reality it doesn’t matter.
This is a positive sleep disorder called speaking in sleep.
It is quite common, especially among children and adolescents.
Surely, more than one of you was told that you spoke at night.
This phenomenon can occur occasionally (once in life, for example, as during high fever), or regularly (every day, once a week, once a month), the next day the child can remember nothing.
There is no single reason that causes this phenomenon.
Often, relationships are sought with other phenomena in sleep, such as nightmares, panic anxiety at night, enuresis noctura (wetting bed at night), talking in sleep, but there is no reason for this.
As we mentioned earlier, it can be due to very high fiber, stressful situations or overload.
